Lost my baby girl Cleo today! She got scared of the noise and ran away…We have been moving so she’s been under stress I would guess…
Any suggestions how to find a lost dog??? 🙏🏻 #lostdog #help We live in Logan Woods, crossing streets Logan blv. And Tallowood Way

I found my baby girl Cleo in the woods close to my house. She still had her leash on which wrapped around the trees and she couldn’t get out… head to toes she was covered in Bur seeds, A bur (also spelled burr) is a seed or dry fruit or infructescence that has hooks or teeth, I added a photo of it. She couldn’t open her eyes, that stuff was all over her face. We had to take her to an animal emergency hospital, where they put her to sleep to shave all the hair and she spend a night there. She’s home happy and safe! ❤️ thank you all for your support! 😘 #foundmybaby

You are a true partner!!! I’m sending my prayers to you and Beata’s family! 🙏🏻 Beata, your Legacy will live forever and your dancing will continue inspiring!!! Not every story is a happy story but as long as it has a good ending, it’s a good story… Things could go so much more worse then they are… Ilana fell off the bed with her whole body weight in to a sharp edge of a solid wood cabinet and spit her forehead open almost 2 inches length … I was sitting right next to her and it happened so fast and unexpected… I drove Ilana and daddy to an emergency room and had to go get my son from his swimming camp. When I pick him up he’s usually all wet in his swim wear, we normally go home straight to the shower, however, this time we drove straight to the hospital with no clothes to change to…. My boy was wet and cold in the hospital… but wonderful staff of NCH Pediatric Emergency Room made our experience so pleasant! Gave Vidas a change of new clothes, made Ilana comfortable & relaxed…They carefully glued her wound to avoid a big scar. @nchpediatricemergencyroom Thanks to you all the doctors and nurses for everything you did! ❤️ we took Ilana staight to shopping after the hospital because that obviously helps to heel 🤣 she’s doing great! Hopefully she will heel fast with no scar 🤞🏻
Just the two of us flying to Chicago 😀 I haven’t been on a plane since august 2019 😱

It was nice to see you Chicago, you are always going to be my first home in United States 🥰 I moved from Lithuania to Chicago in 1997 with 1% of English but with 100% of trust that this will be a new beginning of my dream life… and it definitely is! 💕😀 Outfit from @thebuclub @elisabettafranchi
